data.eml:eml: A revision the Australian species of the ant genus Myrmecina (Hymenoptera: Formicidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Shattuck, Steve (2009): A revision the Australian species of the ant genus Myrmecina (Hymenoptera: Formicidae). Zootaxa 2146: 1-21, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.188674
